All right, I bluffed him' but he knows what I was doing.

1485
01:48:36,384 --> 01:48:37,676
请你的人撤出 由突击队顶替...
We need to rotate your men...

1486
01:48:37,844 --> 01:48:40,554
他认为刚才有人要杀他!
He thinks someone just tried to kill him!

1487
01:48:40,722 --> 01:48:42,223
我们进入 全面攻击
We're going in. Full breach.

1488
01:48:42,682 --> 01:48:45,226
别这样 听我说 全面攻击的话 所有人都会死
Don't do it. Listen. You breach, everyone's gonna die.

1489
01:48:45,393 --> 01:48:47,269
明白吗? 所有人都会死
Understand that? Everyone's gonna die.

1490
01:48:47,437 --> 01:48:50,397
