Maybe that's what some of you wanna have happen, but I don't!

1491
01:48:50,565 --> 01:48:54,068
我被叫来救这个人 带他出来!
I was brought here to save this man's life and bring him out' all right?

1492
01:48:54,236 --> 01:48:56,445
没理由要伤害人质
There's no reason to jeopardize hostages.

1493
01:48:56,613 --> 01:48:57,947
你闭嘴!
Shut up!

1494
01:48:59,950 --> 01:49:03,744
特工 换掉我的人是错的 要换谈判专家 很好
Agent Moran, this is a mistake. You wanna change negotiators' fine.

1495
01:49:03,912 --> 01:49:06,580
给罗曼30秒机会...
But you give Roman a 30-second window of opportunity...

1496
01:49:06,748 --> 01:49:08,207
...他都会利用
...he'll exploit it.

1497
01:49:09,459 --> 01:49:12,253
必须继续包围 我的人已就位 他们能处理
We gotta keep him locked down. My men can handle it.

1498
01:49:12,420 --> 01:49:14,838
领教过他们的处理方法
We've seen what your men can handle.

1499
01:49:15,006 --> 01:49:16,048
让我留下
Please.

1500
01:49:16,216 --> 01:49:18,717
你的人留在原地 我们的人支援...
Your men stay in place. Our men will support yours...

1501
01:49:18,885 --> 01:49:22,137
- ...不过你要执行我们的命令  - 赛比安 你走吧
- ...but you'll execute orders that we give. - You're off' Sabian.

1502
01:49:23,139 --> 01:49:26,976
真不敢相信 满屋子人都想进去杀了他
I can't believe this. I'm just surrounded by people who wanna go in and kill him.

1503
01:49:27,143 --> 01:49:31,397
这人你们称他为朋友 这与我毫无关系!
This is the guy you called your friend. I got nothing invested in this!

1504
01:49:32,607 --> 01:49:34,650
我想知道为什么!
I wonder why that is!

1505
01:49:36,611 --> 01:49:38,320
也许有一天会知道
Maybe someday we'll find out.

1506
01:49:38,488 --> 01:49:40,406
谈判结束了
No more negotiating.

1507
01:49:41,074 --> 01:49:43,951
送塞比安先生上车
Would you please escort Mr. Sabian to his car?

1508
01:49:44,869 --> 01:49:45,953
中尉
Lieutenant.

1509
01:49:46,663 --> 01:49:47,955
这边请
This way' sir.

1510
01:49:48,665 --> 01:49:50,874
急不可待要冲上去 你们自称是他的朋友
Dying to go up. You call yourselves his friends.

1511
01:49:51,042 --> 01:49:54,169
丹尼・罗曼 我是联邦调查局特工格瑞
Danny Roman' this is Agent Grey of the FBI.

1512
01:49:54,588 --> 01:49:57,673
克瑞斯・塞比安已被解除指挥权 现在由我负责
Chris Sabian has been relieved of his command and I'm in charge.

1513
01:49:59,259 --> 01:50:02,553
从现在起停止谈判
As of this mornent, all negotiations are suspended.

1514
01:50:02,721 --> 01:50:05,014
给你5分钟投降...
You have five minutes to surrender...

1515
01:50:05,181 --> 01:50:07,016
...否则我们进去逮捕你
...or we're coming in after you.

1516
01:50:18,987 --> 01:50:21,822
天哪 塞比安进去了
Oh' Christ. Sabian's going in.

1517
01:50:23,491 --> 01:50:25,826
丹尼 是我 我就上来
Danny, it's me. I'm on my way up.

1518
01:50:29,039 --> 01:50:32,958
丹尼 这不是你的错 我们都听见他承认了 有罪的是他不是你
Danny, this wasn't your fault. We all heard him confess. He Was guilty.

1519
01:50:33,918 --> 01:50:35,169
我知道
Yeah.

1520
01:50:36,296 --> 01:50:38,172
无所谓了
Well' what's it matter, Maggie?

1521
01:50:39,007 --> 01:50:41,550
内森死了 尼鲍姆死了
Nate's dead. Niebaum's dead.

1522
01:50:42,469 --> 01:50:43,510
电脑也完了
Computer's dead.

1523
01:50:44,054 --> 01:50:48,432
塞比安上来了
And, look, Sabian is coming upstairs now.

1524
01:50:48,600 --> 01:50:50,684
必须把尼鲍姆的话告诉他
You have to tell him what Niebaum said.

1525
01:50:51,353 --> 01:50:55,397
你要放弃? 那才是犯罪
What, you gonna give up now? Come on, that'd be a crime, man.

1526
01:51:02,364 --> 01:51:04,198
你们都听着...
Listen' all of you...

1527
01:51:05,742 --> 01:51:07,743
...对不起 把你们牵扯进来
...l'm sorry I got you into this.

1528
01:51:08,703 --> 01:51:10,537
很快就要结束了
This'll all be over soon.

1529
01:51:11,915 --> 01:51:15,668
丹尼 接电话 否则我们马上强行进入
Danny, pick up the phone or we will be forced to come in.

1530
01:51:17,087 --> 01:51:20,673
麦琪 请你转告我妻子
Maggie, would you tell my Wife something for me?

1531
01:51:22,342 --> 01:51:24,593
告诉她 我想信守诺言 我努力了
Just tell her I was trying to keep my promise.

1532
01:51:32,977 --> 01:51:34,269
嘿 丹尼
Hey, Danny.

1533
01:51:34,437 --> 01:51:38,190
尼鲍姆经常在家里工作
You know, Niebaum Worked at home just about as much as he worked here.

1534
01:51:40,276 --> 01:51:42,778
内森的录音可能保存在家里
He could've kept Nathan's taps there.

1535
01:51:55,458 --> 01:51:56,959
就你自己?
You alone?

1536
01:51:58,628 --> 01:52:01,797
你必须投降 我无法阻止他们 他们就到了
You gotta surrender now. I can't hold them back. They're coming up.

1537
01:52:01,965 --> 01:52:05,217
