Niebaum told me Hellman, Allen and Argento are involved.

1539
01:52:08,471 --> 01:52:11,473
- 你没有证据  - 他有 尼鲍姆的交待我们都听见了
- You got no proof. - He does. Niebaum confessed. We all heard.

1540
01:52:11,641 --> 01:52:15,269
他们想把我们全杀掉 可你一点没帮我们
They're shooting us one by one and you fuckers aren't helping us.

1541
01:52:15,437 --> 01:52:19,481
- 你到底想不想帮我们?  - 谁下令进攻 贝克?
- Are you gonna help us or what? - Who called for the breach? Beck?

1542
01:52:19,649 --> 01:52:22,484
他说你先开枪 他的人还击 尼鲍姆是个意外
Yeah, but he says you fired first and Niebaum was an accident.

1543
01:52:22,652 --> 01:52:24,737
尼鲍姆不是死于意外 是死于谋杀!
Niebaum Was no accident. He was assassinated.

1544
01:52:24,904 --> 01:52:28,073
子弹全打在他胸口
He's got three bullets, center mass. Look.

1545
01:52:39,669 --> 01:52:43,255
克瑞斯 你不能否认有阴谋
Come on, Chris. You gotta admit something's going on.

1546
01:52:43,423 --> 01:52:46,341
那不重要了 死了两名警官 你杀了其中一个
It doesn't matter. Two cops are dead and you killed one.

1547
01:52:46,509 --> 01:52:50,512
我要赶在他们之前送你和人质出去
I need to get you and these hostages out of here before they come in.

1548
01:52:58,480 --> 01:52:59,521
结束了 丹尼!
Let's end this, Danny!

1549
01:53:15,205 --> 01:53:18,081
他们必须相信我能做到
They had to believe I Was capable of that.

1550
01:53:18,374 --> 01:53:22,127
只死了一个警察 是被陷害我的人打死的
There's only one dead cop up here, killed by the men who tried to set me up.

1551
01:53:23,296 --> 01:53:26,006
内森录下赫尔曼等人的谈话
now, I know Nate tapped Hellman and the others.

1552
01:53:26,174 --> 01:53:29,551
录音带可能在尼鲍姆家里 我能到那里就能结束此事
I think those taps are at Niebaum's. If I get there' I can end this.

1553
01:53:29,719 --> 01:53:33,222
他们会杀了你 除了投降 你无法活着出去
They're gonna kill you. Understand? You got no way out unless you surrender.

1554
01:53:33,389 --> 01:53:35,641
你关掉暖气已给了我出路
You gave me a way out when you shut the heat off.

1555
01:53:35,809 --> 01:53:38,727
你知道你有其他办法能帮我
now, you know there's another way you can help me.

1556
01:53:39,103 --> 01:53:40,687
你看错我了
You were wrong about me.

1557
01:53:42,398 --> 01:53:44,483
我若没看错他们?
What if I'm right about them?

1558
01:53:47,028 --> 01:53:49,363
但你若看错我了?
But What if you're wrong about me?

1559
01:54:04,003 --> 01:54:07,673
麦琪 打开手铐 都去会议室
Maggie. Uncuff yourself. Get in the conference room.

1560
01:54:11,261 --> 01:54:12,845
妈的
Shit.

1561
01:54:15,056 --> 01:54:18,684
开始全面进攻 击毙目标
Initiate full breach. Shoot on sight.

1562
01:54:41,958 --> 01:54:44,293
鲁迪 快走!
Come on, Rudy. Move, move!

1563
01:55:32,926 --> 01:55:35,093
给 麦琪 用这个
Here, Maggie, use this.

1564
01:55:35,595 --> 01:55:39,014
马库斯和鲁迪合用 弄湿它
Markus, split this betWeen you and Rudy. Wet it.

1565
01:55:40,183 --> 01:55:43,352
你知道怎么做 一会将有浓烟和催泪弹
You know the drill. There's gonna be a lot of gas and smoke.

1566
01:55:44,145 --> 01:55:46,021
给我钥匙
Let me have those keys.

1567
01:56:00,995 --> 01:56:04,206
别害怕 马上会来人救你们
Don't be scared. They're coming to save you in a minute.

1568
01:56:04,374 --> 01:56:05,666
关上门
Close the door.

1569
01:56:05,833 --> 01:56:08,293
趴下 趴下 趴在地上
down, down, down. On the ground, now.

1570
01:56:59,762 --> 01:57:01,388
- 快走  - 快走
- Move. - Move now.

1571
01:57:04,851 --> 01:57:06,560
当心!
Look out!

1572
01:57:19,574 --> 01:57:21,241
两人一组
Double up' now! now' now, now!

1573
01:57:51,981 --> 01:57:54,775
找到人质 不见罗曼
Found the hostages. No sign of Roman.

1574
01:57:54,942 --> 01:57:58,153
检查电梯井 所有通风口 地下室
Check the elevator shaft, check every vent, check the basement.

1575
01:57:58,321 --> 01:58:00,906
起来 跟我走!
Come on, get up. Let's go. Let's go!

1576
01:58:04,744 --> 01:58:06,161
找到斯科特
We found Scott.

1577
01:58:07,121 --> 01:58:08,622
他没事
He's alive.

1578
01:58:34,524 --> 01:58:38,193
想证明自己清白 给你个机会
You wanna prove your innocence, here's your chance.

