All right, you wanna get out of here? Follow me.

1582
01:58:55,169 --> 01:58:57,546
只要他在 我们就能找到他
If he's in here, We'll find him.

1583
01:58:57,880 --> 01:58:59,131
他不在
He's not.

1584
01:59:01,425 --> 01:59:02,551
他早走了
He's gone mobile.

1585
01:59:04,846 --> 01:59:09,182
我是指挥官贝克 这次行动再次由我负责
This is Commander Beck. I am now back in charge of this operation.

1586
01:59:09,350 --> 01:59:10,392
你这是干什么?
What are you doing?

1587
01:59:10,560 --> 01:59:13,562
