Why did he go there?

1605
02:01:54,432 --> 02:01:56,224
麦琪?
Maggie?

1606
02:01:58,561 --> 02:02:00,228
他为什么去那里?
Why did he go there?

1607
02:02:17,350 --> 02:02:18,840
(办公室档案: 调查中-监听)

1608
02:02:21,167 --> 02:02:22,250
什么也没有
There's nothing here.

1609
02:02:24,086 --> 02:02:27,547
内森遇害前去见谁? 琳达说了?
Chris. Who did Nate see the night before he Was killed? Did Linda tell you?

1610
02:02:27,715 --> 02:02:30,592
他去找你 可你不在警局
Yeah. He went to see you' but you weren't at the precinct.

1611
02:02:30,760 --> 02:02:32,594
你没时间了
You're running out of time, Danny.

1612
02:02:34,513 --> 02:02:36,639
- 指挥中心 我是指挥官贝克  - 继续
- Dispatch, this is Commander Beck. - Go ahead.

1613
02:02:36,807 --> 02:02:40,602
派空中分队到艾迪逊大街1300号
I need an air unit deployed to the 1300 block of Addison.

1614
02:02:40,770 --> 02:02:45,190
派特别行动队到艾迪逊街口与我汇合
Have available HBT units meet me at the corner of Addison and Iroquois.

1615
02:02:45,441 --> 02:02:47,859
需要一名队长继续清查市府大楼
I also need an HPT supervisor to clear the building.

1616
02:02:48,027 --> 02:02:49,194
收到 随后安排
Copy. Will relay.

1617
02:03:06,420 --> 02:03:08,296
丹尼 什么也没有 一切都结束了
Come on, Danny, there's nothing here. It's over.

1618
02:03:10,549 --> 02:03:13,468
我带你去自首 还有机会
That's it, I'm taking you in' man. You had your chance.

1619
02:03:16,764 --> 02:03:20,600
