I've got two disks with your voices on them. Nate's taps.

1634
02:04:20,453 --> 02:04:21,828
来吧!
Come on down the hall!

1635
02:04:21,996 --> 02:04:24,998
我有15发子弹 每人5发
I got 15 shots here. That's five apiece.

1636
02:04:36,093 --> 02:04:39,053
罗曼 无论你耍什么花招都没有用了
Hell Whatever you're trying to pull, Roman, it's not gonna work.

1637
02:04:39,221 --> 02:04:42,056
趁还没死人 别再胡闹 出来吧
Stop this shit and come out before someone gets killed.

1638
02:04:42,224 --> 02:04:46,394
我知道有人主使 你们自己偷不了那么多钱
Look, I know somebody else was in charge. You couldn't have pulled this off yourself.

1639
02:04:46,562 --> 02:04:49,564
丹尼老兄 你全弄错了
Danny, man, you got this all wrong.

1640
02:04:49,732 --> 02:04:53,359
我没错 你很紧张 阿尔金托
No, I got it right. Is that why you sound so nervous, Argento?

1641
02:04:53,903 --> 02:04:57,071
